Package gwt.g2d.client.graphics.visitor

Contains visitor classes that aids the shape building process.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ShapeVisitor Interface for defining a custom shape/path operation.
 

Class Summary
ArcToVisitor Adds a point to the current path, connected to the previous one by a straight line, then adds a second point to the current path, connected to the previous one by an arc whose properties are described by the arguments.
ArcVisitor Adds points to the subpath such that the arc described by the circumference of the circle described by the arguments, starting at the given start angle and ending at the given end angle, going in the given direction, is added to the path, connected to the previous point by a straight line.
BezierCurveToVisitor Adds the given point to the current path, connected to the previous one by a cubic Bezier curve with the given control points.
BezierCurveVisitor Adds the end point to the current path, connected to the starting point by a cubic Bezier curve with the given control points.
CircleVisitor Draws a circle to the current subpath.
CompositeShapeVisitor A shape that is made up to one or more other shapes.
CubicCurveToVisitor Deprecated.
CubicCurveVisitor Deprecated.
DashedLineVisitor Adds a dashed line segment to the current subpath.
EllipseVisitor Adds a new ellipse to the subpath.
LineSegmentVisitor Adds a line to the current subpath.
LineToVisitor Adds the given point to the current subpath, connected to the previous one by a straight line.
MoveToVisitor Creates a new subpath with the given point.
QuadraticCurveToVisitor Adds the given end point to the current path, connected to the previous one by a quadratic Bezier curve with the given control point.
QuadraticCurveVisitor Adds the given end point to the current path, connected to the start point by a quadratic Bezier curve with the given control point.
RectangleVisitor Adds a new Rectangle to the subpath.
RotateVisitor Rotates clockwise by an angle in radian.
ScaleVisitor Scales the canvas' context.
SetTransformVisitor Sets the current transformation to be the given transformation matrix.
TransformVisitor Multiply the current canvas' transformation by this transformation.
TranslateVisitor Translates by an offset.
 

Package gwt.g2d.client.graphics.visitor Description

Contains visitor classes that aids the shape building process.
